    ...
    2b9cc11f6cfc: Loading layer [===========================>] 176.6kB/176.6kB
    Loaded image: dell-boomi-pks:v0.3.0.dev.3.g6024f1e

To verify that the Docker images are now available:

    $ docker images "dell-boomi-*"
